MIDAS Sound System v0.40 Revision a
A multi-channel digital sound and music
system for C, Pascal and Assembler
programmers. Supports GUS, PAS, SB, WSS
and no sound, plays MOD, S3M and MTM
modules. Can be used with Borland and
Watcom C (16-bit), Borland Pascal 7 and
now also with pure assembler.
FULL SOURCE CODE INCLUDED! Now also all
libraries included in compiled form.
(Extract with subdirectories)
